2002-05-20  Chris Dunlap  <cdunlap@llnl.gov>

	* : Released 0.1.8.

	* server-conf.c: Fixed solaris2.8 portability issues.  Replaced
	  prioritynames[] & facilitynames[] w/ internal portable equivalents.

