	* util-net.c: Fixed bug in host_strerror().  Tweaked get_host_by_name()
	  and get_host_by_addr() to always update h_err.

	* server-conf.c, server-obj.c, server.c, util-net.c: Minor tweaks
	  to appease Solaris compile.

