	* lib/examples/boot_alpha.exp: New.

	* lib/alpha.exp: Added timeout to alpha_do_rmd_cmd.  Added timeout to
	  alpha_do_srm_cmd parms.  Fixed bug in alpha_do_srm_cmd for matching
	  "jumping to bootstrap code".

